      "created_at": "2017-05-26T22:00:00.000Z",
      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1eea9c805c1c027e1438cabd9d9e8c50b99b3b03.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/1eea9c805c1c027e1438cabd9d9e8c50b99b3b03\" title=\"IMG_6309.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1eea9c805c1c027e1438cabd9d9e8c50b99b3b03_2_600x800.JPG\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1eea9c805c1c027e1438cabd9d9e8c50b99b3b03_2_600x800.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1eea9c805c1c027e1438cabd9d9e8c50b99b3b03_2_900x1200.JPG 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1eea9c805c1c027e1438cabd9d9e8c50b99b3b03_2_1200x1600.JPG 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1eea9c805c1c027e1438cabd9d9e8c50b99b3b03_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_6309.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">2448×3264 1.57 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Per librin kemi punuar rreth 3 vjet  para se te shihte driten e botimit. Eshte udhezuesi i pare i plote i shpendeve te Shqiperise me 353 lloje zogjsh, - thote Mirjan Topi, njeri nder autoret e ketij libri qe mbaj ne dore, brenda te cilit mund te shohesh e lexosh disa informacione baze mbi zogjte qe popullojne vendin qe popullojme ne. Eshte nje liber dore, i ngjitur fort ne menyre qe ta marresh me vete kur ben ndonje xhiro ne natyre diku. Por edhe po e mbajte ne shtepi per ta shfletuar per qejf, eshte gjithsesi i kendshem.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/05c24fb6ca639ee1535bbb0683e82e29f58c643d.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/05c24fb6ca639ee1535bbb0683e82e29f58c643d\" title=\"IMG_6599.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/05c24fb6ca639ee1535bbb0683e82e29f58c643d_2_600x800.JPG\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/05c24fb6ca639ee1535bbb0683e82e29f58c643d_2_600x800.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/05c24fb6ca639ee1535bbb0683e82e29f58c643d_2_900x1200.JPG 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/05c24fb6ca639ee1535bbb0683e82e29f58c643d_2_1200x1600.JPG 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/05c24fb6ca639ee1535bbb0683e82e29f58c643d_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_6599.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">2448×3264 1.85 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Mirjan Topi na tregon se me heret eshte botuar nje udhezues i shpendeve dhe gjitareve te Shqiperise por tek ai udhezues ishin pershkruar vetem 219 lloje zogjsh dhe ilustrimi ishte me fotografi dhe jo me vizatime (standarti per hartimin e udhezuesve jane vizatimet). Vizatimet qe ilustrojne pamjen e shpendeve jane realizuar ekskluzivisht per kete udhezues. Kundruesit e zogjve e kane pritur gjate nje liber te tille. Kundrimi i shpendeve eshte aktiviteti i pare ekoturistik ne nivel global dhe gjeneron miliarda dollare te ardhura cdo vit.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/426b01c40981b4e6aa86bacfae93f33c908749a3.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/426b01c40981b4e6aa86bacfae93f33c908749a3\" title=\"IMG_6597.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/426b01c40981b4e6aa86bacfae93f33c908749a3_2_600x800.JPG\" width=\"600\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/426b01c40981b4e6aa86bacfae93f33c908749a3_2_600x800.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/426b01c40981b4e6aa86bacfae93f33c908749a3_2_900x1200.JPG 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/426b01c40981b4e6aa86bacfae93f33c908749a3_2_1200x1600.JPG 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/426b01c40981b4e6aa86bacfae93f33c908749a3_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_6597.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">2448×3264 2.02 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>\n<p>Ky udhezues u shperben te gjithe shqiptarve kudo qe ndodhen, jo vetem ne Shqiperi por edhe ne vendet perreth. Ne Shqiperi ka shume pak kundrues shpendesh, por numri i tyre do vije gjithmone ne rritje, duke marre parasysh dobite shendetsore qe siguron ky aktivitet, ecje dhe qendrime ne ajer te paster. Libri mund te gjendet tek zyrat e PPNEA-se (Rr. Vangjush Furrxhi, Tirane ose: <a href=\"mailto:contact@ppnea.org\">contact@ppnea.org</a>)</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/cbfbb63d4f6b4aee9b6acd7f2ad176e037dad678.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/cbfbb63d4f6b4aee9b6acd7f2ad176e037dad678\" title=\"IMG_6313.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cbfbb63d4f6b4aee9b6acd7f2ad176e037dad678_2_599x800.JPG\" width=\"599\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cbfbb63d4f6b4aee9b6acd7f2ad176e037dad678_2_599x800.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cbfbb63d4f6b4aee9b6acd7f2ad176e037dad678_2_898x1200.JPG 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cbfbb63d4f6b4aee9b6acd7f2ad176e037dad678_2_1198x1600.JPG 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/cbfbb63d4f6b4aee9b6acd7f2ad176e037dad678_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_6313.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">2446×3262 1.39 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div></p>",
